text.div: • Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActRelationshipType where concept is-a SBE

name: ActRelationshipStartsBeforeEnd
title: ActRelationshipStartsBeforeEnd
description: The source Act starts after the end of the target Act (i.e. if we say "ActOne SBE ActTwo", it means that ActOne starts before the end of ActTwo, therefore ActOne is the source and ActTwo is the target).
